		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've tried this sort of thing myself, using a video player that allows you to specify the overlay color and maximizing the video player behind a game. In the same vein, I've also used winamp's overlay option to show an AVS visualization as the background in a text editor. It didn't do very much for me in either case, but I suppose if done well, overlaying game-related content could be nifty.

		

